## EXISTING COMPONENTS

### Atoms
- Button — variants: default, secondary, outlined, ghost, destructive, tonal, tertiary; sizes: default, sm, lg, icon, icon-lg
- Typography — variants: all 15 Material You scale values; textColor prop: default, primary, secondary, muted, error
- Icon — wraps any LucideIcon
- Input — base input with error state
- Badge — variants: default, secondary, outline, error, tonal
- MenuIndicator — 3px active underline bar for tabs
- BreadcrumbItem — ChevronRight icon + label, active/inactive states
- Divider — full-width h-[2px] horizontal rule, bg-outline-variant
- ReduxProvider — wraps Redux store
- ThemeProvider — syncs next-themes ↔ Redux

### Molecules
- ThemeToggle — icon and segmented variants
- NavLink — active-state nav link with underline indicator
- MenuItem — single tab item (MenuIndicator + label), role="tab"
- Menu — horizontal tab bar: {loop of MenuItem} → {ButtonIcon}
- ButtonIcon — theme toggle button composed of Button (variant="tertiary", size="icon-lg") + Icon (Sun/Moon)
- Breadcrumb — ordered list of BreadcrumbItem atoms
- InputText — Input atom (transparent) + Icon atom (Search, 48×48) inside bg-surface-container-high rounded-[28px] container
- PageTitle — Typography (headline-large, on-surface) + Divider (bg-on-surface-variant), column centered, py-5 px-5 gap-4

### Organisms
- Navbar — sticky responsive navbar with mobile drawer
- Footer — simple footer with brand + tagline
- PageHeader — InputText (left, flex-1) + Menu (right) + Divider (bottom); w-full, h-hug

### Templates
- HomeTemplate — landing page: Menu (top-right) + Greeting Label (display-large × 2, max-w-[720px]) + InputText

### Pages
- HomePage — HOC wiring Redux → LandingTemplate

